Purpose:    This package provides an R wrapper to the infochimps.com APIs.

            For more information on the these APIs see http://api.infochimps.com/

Contact:    Drew Conway
Email:      drew.conway@nyu.edu
Date:       2010-11-20

Install:    To install this package from source download the file infochimps_0.1.tar.gz
            and run the following command from the R console:
            
            > install.packages("infochimps_0.1.tar.gz", repos=NULL, type="source")
            
            Or, to install binaries see the official CRAN lisitng:
            
            http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/infochimps/index.html

